       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. GRVAGE2.
      * GRIEVANCE AGEING BY ELAPSED-DAY COUNT (30-DAY WINDOW)
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-DAYS-OPEN              PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-ESCALATE               PIC X(1) VALUE 'N'.
       01  WS-RPT-HEADING            PIC X(7)
           VALUE SPACES.
       01  FILLER                    PIC X(7) VALUE SPACES.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-DAYS-OPEN
           PERFORM 2000-AGE
           DISPLAY 'ESCALATE: ' WS-ESCALATE
           STOP RUN.
       2000-AGE.
           IF WS-DAYS-OPEN > 30
              MOVE 'Y' TO WS-ESCALATE
           END-IF.
